Wiklo is an experimental/hobby project, which is heavily influenced by [[https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/MediaWiki|MediaWiki]]. <div style="float:left; padding: 4px; margin: 0px 8px;">{{nest|logo.svg|width=144px}}</div>

Wiklo is a [[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Static_site_generator|Static Site Generator]]. Every time you edit a page, it immediately generates a static revision, that you can freely move or backup.

Wiklo is a [[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Single-page_application|Single-page Application]]. You can explore all the articles in a single webpage.

Wiklo uses wiki-style texts to make editing easier, while also supporting HTML tags, styles and scripts.

Wiklo utilizes categories to allow simpler exploration.

Wiklo does not use any external library.

Wiklo does not modify your file data.